[FILE:305:descriptions/desc.single]
feh is a versatile and fast image viewer using imlib2, the premier image
file handling library. feh has many features, from simple single file
viewing, to multiple file modes using a slideshow or multiple windows.
feh supports the creation of montages as index prints with many
user-configurable options.


